---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <slot name="head">
    <title>Investment — The Meridian Residences | Luxury Property in South Jakarta</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Explore the investment proposition of The Meridian Residences — market insights, capital appreciation potential, payment schemes, and frequently asked questions for the discerning buyer." />
  </slot>

  <!-- Hero Mini -->
  <section class="pt-48 pb-24 bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard text-center reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Investment</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Investasi</span>
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-primary-ivory leading-tight mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">An Investment in Elevation</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Investasi dalam Elevasi</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        <span class="lang-en">Luxury property in South Jakarta is a proposition of enduring substance — built on scarcity, validated by
        institutions, and positioned for appreciation. The Meridian Residences offers the discerning buyer an
        address that will only grow more valuable with time.</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Properti mewah di Jakarta Selatan adalah proposisi dengan substansi yang bertahan — dibangun di atas kelangkaan, divalidasi oleh institusi, dan diposisikan untuk apresiasi. The Meridian Residences menawarkan kepada pembeli yang cermat sebuah alamat yang hanya akan semakin bernilai seiring waktu.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Market Context -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Market Context</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Konteks Pasar</span>
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-12">
        <span class="lang-en">The Case for South Jakarta</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Kasus untuk Jakarta Selatan</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-gold text-lg">◆</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-3">
            <span class="lang-en">Scarcity That Endures</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Kelangkaan yang Bertahan</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">Land parcels of sufficient scale for a comprehensive luxury development are rare in South Jakarta's
            most established precincts. New supply in these areas is inherently limited, creating a structural
            advantage that supports long-term value retention.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Kavling tanah dengan skala yang memadai untuk pengembangan mewah yang komprehensif sangat langka di kawasan paling mapan di Jakarta Selatan. Pasokan baru di area ini secara inheren terbatas, menciptakan keunggulan struktural yang mendukung retensi nilai jangka panjang.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-gold text-lg">◆</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-3">
            <span class="lang-en">Institutional Density</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Densitas Institusional</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">The neighborhood's value is reinforced by the concentration of international schools, private hospitals,
            diplomatic compounds, and corporate headquarters — institutions that create lasting demand from
            affluent residents.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Nilai kawasan ini diperkuat oleh konsentrasi sekolah internasional, rumah sakit swasta, kompleks diplomatik, dan kantor pusat perusahaan — institusi yang menciptakan permintaan berkelanjutan dari kalangan penghuni kelas atas.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-gold text-lg">◆</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-3">
            <span class="lang-en">Infrastructure Momentum</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Momentum Infrastruktur</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">The MRT North-South line, inner-city toll network improvements, and continued investment in the SCBD
            corridor signal a neighborhood that is still being invested in — and still appreciating.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Jalur MRT Utara-Selatan, peningkatan jaringan tol dalam kota, dan investasi berkelanjutan di koridor SCBD menandakan sebuah kawasan yang masih terus diinvestasikan — dan masih terus terapresiasi.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Capital Appreciation -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="overline mb-6">
          <span class="lang-en">Capital Appreciation</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Apresiasi Modal</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-8">
          <span class="lang-en">The Long View</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Pandangan Jangka Panjang</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">Luxury property investment is, by its nature, a long-duration proposition. The costs of acquisition —
            taxes, legal fees, the friction of capital movement — are not recouped in the short term. The asset class
            rewards patience, and it punishes the impulse to trade.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Investasi properti mewah, secara alamiah, adalah proposisi jangka panjang. Biaya akuisisi — pajak, biaya hukum, friksi pergerakan modal — tidak kembali dalam jangka pendek. Kelas aset ini menghargai kesabaran, dan menghukum dorongan untuk berdagang.</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">For the buyer who can deploy capital with a decade-long horizon, who understands that the finest residences
            in the finest locations tend to appreciate not in straight lines but in punctuated leaps — years of
            stability followed by a step-change driven by an infrastructure opening, a rezoning, a generational
            transfer of land — the Indonesian luxury market offers a proposition that is increasingly difficult to
            find elsewhere in the region: genuine scarcity, in a genuinely growing economy.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Bagi pembeli yang dapat mengerahkan modal dengan cakrawala satu dekade, yang memahami bahwa hunian terbaik di lokasi terbaik cenderung terapresiasi bukan dalam garis lurus, melainkan dalam lompatan-lompatan bertitik — stabilitas bertahun-tahun yang diikuti oleh perubahan bertahap yang didorong oleh pembukaan infrastruktur, perubahan zonasi, transfer lahan antargenerasi — pasar mewah Indonesia menawarkan proposisi yang semakin sulit ditemukan di tempat lain di kawasan ini: kelangkaan yang sesungguhnya, dalam ekonomi yang sungguh-sungguh bertumbuh.</span>
          </p>
          <div class="pull-quote my-10">
            <span class="lang-en">"The asset class rewards patience, and it punishes the impulse to trade."</span>
            <span class="lang-id">"Kelas aset ini menghargai kesabaran, dan menghukum dorongan untuk berdagang."</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Payment Schemes -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Payment Schemes</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Skema Pembayaran</span>
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-12">
        <span class="lang-en">Flexible Acquisition</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Akuisisi Fleksibel</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-3">
            <span class="lang-en">Cash Payment</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Pembayaran Tunai</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            <span class="lang-en">100% Upfront</span>
            <span class="lang-id">100% di Muka</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Full payment at signing, offering the most straightforward path to ownership with a streamlined
            documentation process and the earliest possible handover timeline.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-3">
            <span class="lang-en">Staged Payment</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Pembayaran Bertahap</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            <span class="lang-en">Over Construction Period</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Selama Periode Konstruksi</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Payments staggered across construction milestones, allowing buyers to align their capital deployment
            with the project's progress and manage cash flow with precision.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8 card-lift">
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-3">
            <span class="lang-en">Financing Available</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Pembiayaan Tersedia</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gold text-sm font-medium mb-4">
            <span class="lang-en">Through Partner Banks</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Melalui Bank Mitra</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Competitive mortgage facilities are available through our network of partner financial institutions,
            with terms tailored to the specific profile of the buyer and the property.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Accordion -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan</span>
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-12">
        <span class="lang-en">Your Questions Answered</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Pertanyaan Anda Terjawab</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm group">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-primary-ivory text-lg flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="lang-en">What title types are available for The Meridian Residences?</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Jenis hak milik apa yang tersedia untuk The Meridian Residences?</span>
            <span class="text-gold text-xl transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">The Meridian Residences offers both Hak Milik (Right of Ownership) for Indonesian citizens and Hak Pakai
            (Right of Use) for international buyers, with secure tenure and rights of renewal as provided under
            Indonesian law. We recommend engaging independent legal counsel to understand the implications of each
            title type for your specific circumstances.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">The Meridian Residences menawarkan Hak Milik untuk warga negara Indonesia dan Hak Pakai untuk pembeli internasional, dengan masa kepemilikan yang aman dan hak perpanjangan sebagaimana diatur dalam hukum Indonesia. Kami menyarankan untuk melibatkan penasihat hukum independen guna memahami implikasi dari setiap jenis hak milik sesuai dengan keadaan spesifik Anda.</span>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm group">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-primary-ivory text-lg flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="lang-en">What is the expected completion and handover timeline?</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Berapa perkiraan jadwal penyelesaian dan serah terima?</span>
            <span class="text-gold text-xl transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">Construction is underway with an anticipated completion within 36 months from groundbreaking. Specific
            handover dates for individual residences will be confirmed as the project progresses through each
            construction milestone.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Konstruksi sedang berlangsung dengan perkiraan penyelesaian dalam 36 bulan sejak peletakan batu pertama. Tanggal serah terima spesifik untuk masing-masing hunian akan dikonfirmasi seiring proyek berjalan melalui setiap tonggak konstruksi.</span>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm group">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-primary-ivory text-lg flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="lang-en">Are there restrictions on foreign ownership?</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Apakah ada pembatasan untuk kepemilikan asing?</span>
            <span class="text-gold text-xl transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">Foreign buyers may acquire residences under Hak Pakai title, which provides secure tenure with renewal
            rights. The specific terms, duration, and conditions are governed by Indonesian property law and
            regulations. We facilitate introductions to qualified legal advisors who specialise in international
            property transactions.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Pembeli asing dapat memperoleh hunian dengan hak Pakai, yang memberikan masa kepemilikan yang aman dengan hak perpanjangan. Ketentuan, durasi, dan persyaratan spesifik diatur oleh hukum dan regulasi properti Indonesia. Kami memfasilitasi perkenalan dengan penasihat hukum berkualifikasi yang berspesialisasi dalam transaksi properti internasional.</span>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm group">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-primary-ivory text-lg flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="lang-en">What service charges and ongoing costs should I anticipate?</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Biaya layanan dan biaya berkelanjutan apa yang harus saya antisipasi?</span>
            <span class="text-gold text-xl transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">Monthly service charges cover the maintenance and operation of all common areas, amenities, security,
            and building management. A detailed schedule of charges is provided during the acquisition process.
            These charges are structured to ensure The Meridian maintains the highest standards of presentation
            and service.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Biaya layanan bulanan mencakup pemeliharaan dan pengoperasian seluruh area bersama, fasilitas, keamanan, dan manajemen gedung. Rincian biaya disediakan selama proses akuisisi. Biaya ini disusun untuk memastikan The Meridian mempertahankan standar tertinggi dalam presentasi dan layanan.</span>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm group">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-primary-ivory text-lg flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="lang-en">Can I customise the interior finishes of my residence?</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Dapatkah saya menyesuaikan finishing interior hunian saya?</span>
            <span class="text-gold text-xl transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">Yes. The Meridian offers a curated range of finish palettes and customisation options, allowing residents
            to personalise their spaces within a framework that maintains the integrity of the architectural vision.
            Our design team works closely with each buyer to accommodate preferences in stone selection, joinery
            finishes, and lighting configurations.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Ya. The Meridian menawarkan rangkaian palet finishing dan opsi penyesuaian yang dikurasi, memungkinkan penghuni untuk mempersonalisasi ruang mereka dalam kerangka yang menjaga integritas visi arsitektur. Tim desain kami bekerja sama dengan setiap pembeli untuk mengakomodasi preferensi dalam pemilihan batu, finishing kayu, dan konfigurasi pencahayaan.</span>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm group">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-primary-ivory text-lg flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="lang-en">Is The Meridian Residences a completed project?</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Apakah The Meridian Residences sudah merupakan proyek yang selesai?</span>
            <span class="text-gold text-xl transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="lang-en">The Meridian Residences is currently under construction. The Sales Gallery is open for private viewings
            by appointment, where you can experience the material selections, review floor plans, and discuss
            acquisition in detail with our team.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">The Meridian Residences saat ini sedang dalam tahap konstruksi. Galeri Penjualan terbuka untuk kunjungan pribadi dengan janji temu, di mana Anda dapat merasakan langsung pilihan material, meninjau denah lantai, dan mendiskusikan akuisisi secara mendetail dengan tim kami.</span>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Prospectus CTA -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard text-center reveal">
      <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-6">
          <span class="lang-en">Download the Prospectus</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Unduh Prospektus</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-300 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          <span class="lang-en">Access the complete investment prospectus — including detailed financial projections, market analysis,
          and technical specifications — by registering your interest below.</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Akses prospektus investasi lengkap — termasuk proyeksi keuangan terperinci, analisis pasar, dan spesifikasi teknis — dengan mendaftarkan minat Anda di bawah ini.</span>
        </p>
        <a href="/contact#brochure" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-lang-en="Download Prospectus" data-lang-id="Unduh Prospektus">Download Prospectus</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
